dcterms:description: A dataset containing data from a Panasonic 18650 battery cell with lithium nickel cobalt aluminium oxide (NCA) chemistry, subjected to different drive cycles at various temperatures (0 °C to 25 °C). The dataset includes parameters such as voltage, current, temperature, and State of Charge (SOC).
dcterms:title: Panasonic 18650 battery cell dataset

dcterms:creator: P. J. Kollmeyer
dcterms:description: A collection of drive cycles including HWFET, LA92, US06, and UDDS, used to simulate real-life driving conditions for electric vehicles. These cycles provide a diverse set of load profiles for battery testing.
dcterms:title: HWFET, LA92, US06, and UDDS drive cycles
